<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>Articles | MindEase</title>
<meta name="description" content="Explore mental health articles about anxiety, depression, stress management, and emotional wellbeing.">
<style>
body{
    font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
    margin:0;
    background:#f5f7fb;
}
header{
    background:linear-gradient(135deg,#4f46e5,#06b6d4);
    color:white;
    padding:40px 20px;
    text-align:center;
}
.search-box{
    max-width:600px;
    margin:20px auto;
}
.search-box input{
    width:100%;
    padding:15px;
    border:none;
    border-radius:10px;
    font-size:16px;
}
.container{
    max-width:1200px;
    margin:40px auto;
    display:grid;
    grid-template-columns:repeat(auto-fit,minmax(280px,1fr));
    gap:25px;
    padding:20px;
}
.card{
    background:white;
    border-radius:15px;
    padding:25px;
    box-shadow:0 4px 15px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
    transition:0.3s;
}
.card:hover{
    transform:translateY(-5px);
}
.card h2{
    margin-top:0;
}
.card a{
    display:inline-block;
    margin-top:15px;
    text-decoration:none;
    padding:10px 18px;
    background:#4f46e5;
    color:white;
    border-radius:8px;
}
footer{
    text-align:center;
    padding:30px;
    background:#111827;
    color:white;
}
</style>
</head>
<body>

<header>
    <h1>MindEase Articles</h1>
    <p>Evidence-based mental health articles and resources.</p>

    <div class="search-box">
        <input type="text" id="searchInput" placeholder="Search articles...">
    </div>
</header>

<div class="container" id="articlesContainer">

<div class="card">
<h2>Anxiety Symptoms and Treatment</h2>
<p>Learn about anxiety symptoms, causes and treatment options.</p>
<a href="articles/anxiety.html">Read Article</a>
</div>

<div class="card">
<h2>Depression Warning Signs</h2>
<p>Understand early symptoms of depression and available support.</p>
<a href="articles/depression.html">Read Article</a>
</div>

<div class="card">
<h2>How to Reduce Stress Naturally</h2>
<p>Simple techniques to manage stress and improve wellbeing.</p>
<a href="articles/stress.html">Read Article</a>
</div>

<div class="card">
<h2>Understanding Panic Attacks</h2>
<p>Recognize panic attack symptoms and coping strategies.</p>
<a href="articles/panic-attacks.html">Read Article</a>
</div>

</div>

<footer>
© 2026 MindEase. All Rights Reserved.
</footer>

<script>
const searchInput=document.getElementById("searchInput");
searchInput.addEventListener("keyup",function(){
const filter=this.value.toLowerCase();
const cards=document.querySelectorAll(".card");
cards.forEach(card=>{
card.style.display=card.innerText.toLowerCase().includes(filter) ? "block" : "none";
});
});
</script>

</body>
</html>
